  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Timber harvesting (commissioning) event for a single serialized log.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries: GS1 product master data plus product-level eudr:",
    "attributes (commodityType, timberProductType, speciesScientificName / CommonName)",
    "on the product entry, and plot-specific eudr: attributes (forestManagementUnit,",
    "areaHectares) on the place entry.",
    "ilmd carries the lot-specific eudr:volumeCubicMeters — the measured volume of THIS",
    "particular log, fixed at commissioning time and unique to this item.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: eudr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/eudr/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
